---
title: Easy Sweet Soy Beef & Veggie Stir-Fry with Charred Corn Rice & Peanuts
description: A beef stir-fry isn’t complete without veggies and a sticky dark sauce. Make sure it coats everything, because this stir-fry sauce is addictive. You'll need a fluffy rice to help soak it up so nothing is left in the bowl when you’re done.
